/user

  • tests the router connection

    GET
    GET 
    /hello
    Sample request
    curl 
    /hello
    curl -X GET "http://visionarchive.io/hello"
    Response 200 OK
    body 
    {
  "message": "hello world"
}

  • Set rating on a item for this user. user id, item id, rating (int: 0, 1, 2, 3, 4 or 5)

    PUT
    PUT 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    content-type: application/json
content-length: 61

    {
  "user": "33007513382472098000",
  "item": "W00003705",
  "rating": 1
}
    curl -X PUT -H "content-type: application/json" -H "content-length: 61" -d '{"user":"33007513382472098000","item":"W00003705","rating":1}' "http://visionarchive.io/user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705"
    Response 200 OK
    body 
    {
  "__v": 0,
  "user": "33007513382472098000",
  "rating": 1,
  "item": "W00003705",
  "_id": "57602fb6210ac8e3dab36885"
}

  • Only accepts one rating per user

    PUT
    PUT 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    content-type: application/json
content-length: 61

    {
  "user": "33007513382472098000",
  "item": "W00003705",
  "rating": 3
}
    curl -X PUT -H "content-type: application/json" -H "content-length: 61" -d '{"user":"33007513382472098000","item":"W00003705","rating":3}' "http://visionarchive.io/user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705"
    Response 200 OK
    body 
    {
  "_id": "57602fb6210ac8e3dab36885",
  "user": "33007513382472098000",
  "rating": 3,
  "item": "W00003705",
  "__v": 0
}

  • Only accepts ratings between 0 and 5

    PUT
    PUT 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    content-type: application/json
content-length: 64

    {
  "user": "33007513382472098000",
  "item": "W00003705",
  "rating": 6.91
}
    curl -X PUT -H "content-type: application/json" -H "content-length: 64" -d '{"user":"33007513382472098000","item":"W00003705","rating":6.91}' "http://visionarchive.io/user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705"

  • Un-set rating on item for this user item id, user id

    DEL
    DELETE 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705
    content-type: application/json
content-length: 50

    {
  "user": "33007513382472098000",
  "item": "W00003705"
}
    curl -X DELETE -H "content-type: application/json" -H "content-length: 50" -d '{"user":"33007513382472098000","item":"W00003705"}' "http://visionarchive.io/user/33007513382472098000/item/W00003705"
    Response 200 OK
    body 
    {
  "message": "Rating deleted."
}
